import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import './App.css' function Homepage() { const [user, setUser] = useState(null); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { const token = localStorage.getItem('token'); if (!token) { navigate('/login'); } else { axios.get('/api/auth/verify', { headers: { 'Authorization': token } }) .then(response => { if (response.status !== 200) { navigate('/login'); } else { navigate('/homepage'); } }) .catch(() => { navigate('/login'); }); } }, [navigate]); return ( //
